# Web Design Extractor Skill

This project includes a custom skill for extracting and reproducing website designs.

## When to Use

Use this skill when the user asks to:
- Analyze a website's design
- Extract a design system from a URL
- Create a design guide from a webpage
- Reproduce/clone a website's look and feel
- Understand and replicate visual design patterns

## How to Use

Read the skill file at `.cursor/skills/web-design-extractor/SKILL.md` for complete instructions.

## Quick Reference

| Script | Purpose |
|--------|---------|
| `extract_design.py` | Extract CSS and design tokens from URL |
| `capture_screenshot.py` | Capture viewport and full-page screenshots |
| `generate_guide.py` | Generate design guide markdown |
| `compare_pages.py` | Compare screenshots for pixel-perfect validation |

## Dependencies

```bash
pip install playwright pillow numpy
playwright install chromium
```
